---
title: Creamy Leek and Mustard Chicken with Green Beans and Mashed Potatoes
description: Why did the chicken cross the road? In this case, it’s definitely to get to the mustard on the other side, because, boy, do those two make a mean combination! We’ve added some tender, crunchy green beans and creamy potatoes to soften the mustardy goodness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-leek-and-mustard-chicken-f2b05a8c.jpg
